<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="1438" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="14.[160,1155,1544,1708]" box="[160,300,1544,1570]" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,300,1544,1570]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Distribution</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[160,1155,1544,1708]" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">
This genus is recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[475,615,1579,1604]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
for the first time. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Loew" authorityYear="1857" box="[813,990,1579,1604]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Chrysotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="suavis">
<emphasis box="[813,990,1579,1604]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Chrysotus suavis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[229,331,1614,1639]" name="Germany" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Germany</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[404,500,1614,1639]" name="Hungary" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Hungary</collectingCountry>
and is further recorded from many countries of the Palaearctic Region including 
<collectingCountry box="[494,575,1649,1674]" name="Algeria" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Algeria</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[589,656,1649,1674]" name="Egypt" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Egypt</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[669,714,1649,1674]" name="Iraq" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Iraq</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[728,773,1649,1674]" name="Iran" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Iran</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[787,848,1649,1674]" name="Israel" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Israel</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[861,959,1649,1674]" name="Morocco" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Morocco</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1022,1100,1649,1674]" name="Turkey" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">Turkey</collectingCountry>
; it is excluded from the Afrotropical Region (
<collectingCountry box="[606,723,1683,1708]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438">DR Congo</collectingCountry>
) by 
<bibRefCitation author="Grichanov IYa" box="[772,965,1683,1708]" pageId="14" pageNumber="1438" pagination="1 - 152" refId="ref12605" refString="Grichanov IYa. 2018. An annotated catalogue of Afrotropical Dolichopodoidae (Diptera). St. Petersburg: VIZR (Plant Protection News Suppl. 25); p. 1 - 152." type="journal article" year="2018">Grichanov (2018)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
